&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Original Meter" class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="179px" data-flex-grow="74" height="1707" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://svtter.cn/p/poor-performance-of-large-models-on-specific-tasks/pics/meter-2.jpg" srcset="https://svtter.cn/p/poor-performance-of-large-models-on-specific-tasks/pics/meter-2_hu_bcbd419fdfe58b59.jpg 800w, https://svtter.cn/p/poor-performance-of-large-models-on-specific-tasks/pics/meter-2.jpg 1280w" width="1280"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
